The paper discusses a novel active learning framework for classification tasks, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The proposed method involves ranking and scoring samples based on multiple query criteria, which can be related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), or information retrieval (cs.IR) tasks.
